data.description: Location, location, location! This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is surrounded by mature trees in the established neighborhood of San Jose Forest. With vaulted ceilings, an open floor plan and huge enclosed porch, this home was just updated with a new HVAC system. The fully fenced backyard, abundant closet space and cozy fireplace make this home an Anastasia Island oasis. You'll be able to drive or even bike to the famous locations such as St. Augustine beach, the nation wide known Amphitheatre,  restaurants, bars, shopping and even Flagler Hospital within five minutes. Zoned for the highly south after R.B. Hunt Elementary School district and ability to rent this property short term, makes this the ideal property for any buyer! Schedule your showing today!
